These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, bridge, domino
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing domino##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Game   | bridge | canasta | mah-jongg | domino |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, dancer, architect, accountant
1. the accountant is on the far right##1
2. the social-worker is on the far left##1
3. the architect is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Job   | social-worker | architect | dancer | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, crime, mystery, fantasy
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | drama | crime | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
