.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, marigold, daffodil
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
2. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |    3    |    4    |
| Flower   | marigold | daffodil | sunflower | amaryllis |

 